Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's begin this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that there's only seven of them, {\alpha&HFF&}one of the eight must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that there's only seven of them, one of the eight must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose they've most likely... {\alpha&HFF&}killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose they've most likely... killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to advance the Yotsuba Group's development further, {\alpha&HFF&}whom should we kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to advance the Yotsuba Group's development further, whom should we kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! {\alpha&HFF&}It's exactly like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! It's exactly like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... {\alpha&HFF&}at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, there are a few things we need to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, we need to address Hatori's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I'm honest, I'm kind of relieved that Hatori is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has clearly shown us what will happen to those who try to leave this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe everyone here has understood the significance of Hatori's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let this be a lesson to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Erald Coil's report...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of their members has died, and that's all they've got to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this report is what our $5 million paid for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't uncovered any vital information, such as L's face or name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this guy, Coil, really going to be of any use?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the report he warns us not to underestimate L's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Given your current pace... {\alpha&HFF&}particularly the fact that the deaths which benefit the Yotsuba Group occur every Friday and Saturday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Given your current pace... particularly the fact that the deaths which benefit the Yotsuba Group occur every Friday and Saturday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, it's possible that L will connect this to Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to figure this much out about us, Coil's a pretty capable guy in my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we need to reconsider our current plan of killing off people towards the end of each week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}This is incredible. The confessions just seem to keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is incredible. {\alpha&HFF&}The confessions just seem to keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is incredible. The confessions just seem to keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:02:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, with this recording, we'd be able to arrest all seven of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, this is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's not being very versatile with this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should at least attempt to spread them out over the course of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that since Coil's realized this, it's going to be too risky to carry on killing at our current pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, we've got to be more discreet, {\alpha&HFF&}and ensure that no one else finds out about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, we've got to be more discreet, and ensure that no one else finds out about this.
