Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the Yotsuba Group, among other companies, will lose a lot of clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
