Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who, {\alpha&HFF&}we need to contact one of them and force them to call off the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who, we need to contact one of them and force them to call off the murders.
