Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, if Kira really is one of those seven, {\alpha&HFF&}is it fair to assume that if we call one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, if Kira really is one of those seven, is it fair to assume that if we call one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the chance of them being Kira is one in seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that there'd be two at most, {\alpha&HFF&}so I'd say two out of seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that there'd be two at most, so I'd say two out of seven.
