Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to call, use the phones in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't be traced or tapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideally we would just wipe out all the executives of our rival enterprises, one after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the fastest method, but I guess it doesn't work like that...
