Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire meeting has been recorded by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You began the talks with Hatori's death, {\alpha&HFF&}and then went on to discuss who you should kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You began the talks with Hatori's death, and then went on to discuss who you should kill.
