Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not Kira or negotiating directly with them, {\alpha&HFF&}I can make a deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not Kira or negotiating directly with them, I can make a deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A deal?!
