Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that will prove too difficult for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
