Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell people about this phone call, it'll just cause a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll do you no favors, and you'll all be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}my aim is to go head-to-head with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my aim is to go head-to-head with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully... {\alpha&HFF&}if L beats Kira, you won't be charged; if Kira beats L, you get to continue your affluent life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully... if L beats Kira, you won't be charged; {\alpha&HFF&}if Kira beats L, you get to continue your affluent life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully... if L beats Kira, you won't be charged; if Kira beats L, you get to continue your affluent life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just play along with both sides and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L or Kira, whoever wins, you can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way for you to lose... {\alpha&HFF&}is if you're caught right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way for you to lose... is if you're caught right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already figured out what my final decision has got to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Namikawa? {\alpha&HFF&}Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Namikawa? Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my men has messed up. I'll have to deal with it on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the interruption. {\alpha&HFF&}Let's get back on topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the interruption. Let's get back on topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for when we're going to kill the E.L.F. members and Zenzai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we give Coil a month, {\alpha&HFF&}and if he still hasn't discovered L's identity by then, we'll kill them off on random dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we give Coil a month, and if he still hasn't discovered L's identity by then, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll kill them off on random dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we give Coil a month, and if he still hasn't discovered L's identity by then, we'll kill them off on random dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll give him another month, and repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once L is out of the way, we can resume killing two or three each fortnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, our main priority should be to deal with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {\alpha&HFF&}It's true that if we deal with L, we'll have no one left in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's true that if we deal with L, we'll have no one left in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, we should tread carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it can't hurt to play it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we'll give Coil a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No objections!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L should be satisfied with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we'll continue to meet on a fortnightly basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, you really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did you manage to postpone the killings, {\alpha&HFF&}but we might even be able to obtain information from Namikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did you manage to postpone the killings, but we might even be able to obtain information from Namikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your methods are similar to mine, {\alpha&HFF&}and you managed to think of this before I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your methods are similar to mine, and you managed to think of this before I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, {\alpha&HFF&}you may be able to carry on the name of "L".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, you may be able to carry on the name of "L".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a month to deduce who Kira is, and to find the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The challenge begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, since you were the first to notice the Yotsuba Group, {\alpha&HFF&}it's fair to say that you may be more capable than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, since you were the first to notice the Yotsuba Group, it's fair to say that you may be more capable than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that you may be able to handle it, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would you succeed me as L?
Comment: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to die, would you succeed me... {\alpha&HFF&}with the name of "L"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to die, would you succeed me... with the name of "L"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's Kira, and is putting on an act, he'll definitely answer "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're wearing these, we'll die together--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sorry, but I'm going to have to speak your thoughts aloud to everyone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, I'm sorry, but I'm going to have to speak your thoughts aloud to everyone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki is thinking that if I were Kira, then either I still am Kira right now and just pretending otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or Kira's power have passed to someone else, and right now I have no recollection of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the two patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is the former, and I am just acting, then he can never take these handcuffs off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}even if I wasn't acting, he probably wouldn't remove the handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even if I wasn't acting, he probably wouldn't remove the handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's thinking that I was Kira, and even though that power may have passed to someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have set things up so that the power will return to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, {\alpha&HFF&}it's not that I was simply being manipulated,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's not that I was simply being manipulated,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather, I may have transferred the power to someone, and have planned to regain it once the suspicions against me had been lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... {\alpha&HFF&}he knew exactly what I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... he knew exactly what I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki was thinking that, "after L's position is his, Yagami Light will become Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To gain the same status as L and be in a position to even manipulate the police... {\alpha&HFF&}while secretly being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To gain the same status as L and be in a position to even manipulate the police... while secretly being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you think that I'm capable of achieving this... {\alpha&HFF&}no, in fact you are saying I would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you think that I'm capable of achieving this... no, in fact you are saying I would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you think now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, you must have realized that I'm not acting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that if you were putting on an act to take my position you wouldn't be revealing your plan to everyone, {\alpha&HFF&}am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that if you were putting on an act to take my position you wouldn't be revealing your plan to everyone, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly believe that after catching the current Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd go on to become Kira... A murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly believe that after catching the current Kira, I'd go on to become Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}A murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly believe that after catching the current Kira, I'd go on to become Kira... A murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really see me as that kind of human being?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! {\alpha&HFF&}An eye for an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! An eye for an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just call this a draw and be done with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. {\alpha&HFF&}For now, we've got to catch the Kira that's right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. For now, we've got to catch the Kira that's right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're wearing these handcuffs, you can't have any complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, we've only got a month left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can use the footage of that meeting as evidence to arrest those seven, won't the judging of criminals stop as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Unfortunately"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can't be certain that Kira is among those seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is only connected to them, and we arrest them, then all that will happen is that those seven will be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we know for sure that one of those seven is Kira, there's no point in arresting them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even if Kira is among them, it's difficult to say who it is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But if we can't say that Kira is definitely not among those seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But if we can't say that Kira is definitely not among those seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a possibility that if we arrest them, the murders will cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as my father says. {\alpha&HFF&}There is that possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as my father says. There is that possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, {\alpha&HFF&}I think I'll chase Kira on my own after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I think I'll chase Kira on my own after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you use these headquarters and I'll continue to use them myself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san and the rest of you can continue to pursue Kira as you wish, using your own methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll investigate using my own methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we do this, it'll just end in arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you insist on narrowing it down before you pursue Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't solve this case unless Kira is caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying that there's no point in stopping the deaths of the criminals in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but unless we expose all truths to the light, Kira will appear again, and consequently, the victims will increase in numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, {\alpha&HFF&}it's my belief that we need to confirm Kira's identity through those seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, it's my belief that we need to confirm Kira's identity through those seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against the arrest of those seven, {\alpha&HFF&}so if you're planning to do it, it's your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against the arrest of those seven, so if you're planning to do it, it's your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pursure Kira by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a month. {\alpha&HFF&}It'll depend on which of us is fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a month. It'll depend on which of us is fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Amane's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Light-kun, I know you're on your father's side, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'll need you to come with me as I can't remove the handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Light-kun, I know you're on your father's side, but I'll need you to come with me as I can't remove the handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Is it okay if we go on a date today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Ryuuzaki-san has got to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you love Light-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you also admire Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you had to choose between them, who would you pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! {\alpha&HFF&}Light, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Light, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm grateful to Kira and I've wanted to meet them in the past, but that isn't love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely have to be Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Light-kun, you want to catch Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}Don't you, Light-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Light-kun, you want to catch Kira. Don't you, Light-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to catch them. {\alpha&HFF&}Now, what do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to catch them. Now, what do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light wants to catch them, then I want them caught too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if it was possible, you would want to be of use to Light-kun, and help him investigate, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}-_-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! {\alpha&HFF&}Misa would do anything for Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Misa would do anything for Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a minute! {\alpha&HFF&}What are you planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a minute! What are you planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get Erald Coil to report to those seven that he's got a lead that suggests that Amane Misa may know L in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that "Amane Misa was interrogated on suspicion of being the second Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they think that there's a chance that Amane Misa knows L,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll definitely employ her to be in their commercials, and attempt to question her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time Matsuda messed up, {\alpha&HFF&}he did ask for her to be hired for a commercial, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time Matsuda messed up, he did ask for her to be hired for a commercial, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that would put you in danger, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about my safety? Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Misa would do anything for you. This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}if they think you know L, they'll try any means possible to get you to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Misa, if they think you know L, {\alpha&HFF&}they'll try any means possible to get you to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Misa, if they think you know L, they'll try any means possible to get you to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! No matter how much they torture Misa, she won't say a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that Kira can manipulate people before their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a real chance that they'll manipulate Misa into talking before killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, {\alpha&HFF&}if they kill L, they'll no longer have a use for her, and will kill her in order to silence her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if they kill L, they'll no longer have a use for her, and will kill her in order to silence her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as we win, Misa-san won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, {\alpha&HFF&}as long as we're connected by these handcuffs, we'll share the same destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, as long as we're connected by these handcuffs, we'll share the same destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, you'll die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that happens, the saddest person will be Misa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either Light-kun and I die, {\alpha&HFF&}or we catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either Light-kun and I die, or we catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch Kira! I can't live in a world without Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuzaki! You're going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm in a hurry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time. I'm in a hurry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Amane Misa's willpower and love for Light-kun are beyond comparison in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa may have been misjudging you until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling you a pervert and so on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality, you actually understand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, {\alpha&HFF&}Misa-san is an excellent lady, completely worthy of Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Misa-san is an excellent lady, completely worthy of Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might fall for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, I'm not so keen on that... how about we say "we're friends", Ryuuzaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made another friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! All of Light's friends are Misa's friends too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Misa never sells out her friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us will combine our powers and catch that Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well actually, {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami-kun wants to approach the investigation with his father in a different way than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well actually, Yagami-kun wants to approach the investigation with his father in a different way than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it'll just be the two of us: Misa-san and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What's up with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You play pretty dirty, Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}you're giving me no choice but to join this investiga--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You play pretty dirty, Ryuuzaki... you're giving me no choice but to join this investiga--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light's joining too! It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it! {\alpha&HFF&}I'm against the methods used in this investigation itself. It's too dangerous for Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it! I'm against the methods used in this investigation itself. {\alpha&HFF&}It's too dangerous for Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it! I'm against the methods used in this investigation itself. It's too dangerous for Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}thank you so much for thinking of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... thank you so much for thinking of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me do this. Misa wants to be useful to you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to help you, so that you'll love me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Misa will quite happily die for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, given the current situation, it'll prove difficult to arrest those seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any good ideas, {\alpha&HFF&}Mogi? Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any good ideas, Mogi? {\alpha&HFF&}Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any good ideas, Mogi? Matsuda?
